  "text": "At the same time, from the perspective of empirical analysis, recently developed non-linear tools were able to characterize variability of local brain dynamics and interaction effects of distributed brain activity (see [CITATION_1] for a review). Informationtheoretic techniques provide a model-free non-linear approach to address both issues [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
